HEADWORD: soul kiss
<hw>soul" kiss`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kiss in which
both parties have their mouths open and pressed together, and the tongue
of one or both is maneuvered within the mouth of the other.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> French kiss, deep kiss.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Soulless</ent>⟦br⟧
